universum.studios.websocket.adapter

Class BaseWebSocketDelegate

  • java.lang.Object
    • universum.studios.websocket.adapter.BaseWebSocketDelegate
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WebSocketDelegate

    public abstract class BaseWebSocketDelegate
extends Object
implements WebSocketDelegate
    A WebSocketDelegate implementation which is recommended to be used as base for all concrete WebSocketDelegate implementations.

    This base class implements mainly logic for registration and un-registration of OnConnectionListenera and OnIncomingFrameListeners.

    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky
